{"tid":717741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"找錢碰到女客手變性騷離職　胖工讀生嘆「人醜性騷擾」","createTime":"2018-06-26T09:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T11:35:31.000Z","uid":122,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b4ede0b81b7ba844d48c3a145cb15f99cc428cda","tid":717741,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:15:56.000Z","msg":"這樣算性騷擾？一名自稱是肥胖小小工讀生的加油站員工昨在臉書社團「爆怨公社」發文，表示因為找零錢時碰到女騎士的手背，事後竟被投訴性騷擾，對方還稱「希望不要再有下一位女孩受害」。員工控訴，之後公司還要求他自己離職，他憤怒無奈一度想自殺，但又不想帶著這個屈辱死去，目前已經申請離職，但他也感嘆：「人帥真好 ，人醜性騷擾這句話我明白了。」<br />\n<br />\n員工坦承當時確實有碰到女騎士手背，但他解釋，是因為當天很忙、客人很多，之前已經撿錢撿發票撿到腰痠背痛，為了避免客人再沒接好找的錢和發票，所以才雙手找錢，想不到碰到女騎士短短一秒鐘就讓對方覺得不舒服。他表示自己覺得鬱悶、無助、無奈，認為這樣的公司他也不想待了，「我只想清白的活著」，更自嘲「會努力減肥的」。<br />\n<br />\n其他網友紛紛留言表示「如果這樣都算性騷擾，那我看她應該要去躲在山裡會比較安全」、「女生手小確實會有些加油員會雙手幫忙托」、「有精神疾病才會這樣覺得性騷擾吧」、「以後一人發一支夾子收錢找錢，錢掉了客人自己撿」、「以後找錢都用撒的好了，整個仙女散花自己撿」。<br />\n<br />\n至於業者是否因此要求員工離職，據《ETtoday新聞雲》報導，中油油品行銷事業部副執行長鄒覺非表示，站長只是先請工讀生休息幾天，並沒有要求他離職，雖然現在工讀生已請辭，但仍希望解開誤會。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180626/1380136/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180626%2F1380136%2F&d=xBUnGN%2F33Zh0ziXbQfL0yv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=5e79bcd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180626%2F1380136%2F&h=18a4f9de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180626/1380136/</a>"},{"pid":"365d2029e60f132ae32472139dc9d99d7609c81d","tid":717741,"uid":122,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:16:36.000Z","msg":"女律師：大叔摸女性肩膀算性騷擾　但福山雅治、木村拓哉摸就OK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/641872/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/641872/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7f9f3671ce52fd7102e3292d554d81f0c29cc3f7","tid":717741,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:17:07.000Z","msg":"條女都唔好得幾多<br />\nsuper打個和算啦"},{"pid":"31669f8052e95d2f86e7b3f8a6a0893df195d9c7","tid":717741,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:17:13.000Z","msg":"明明就係性騷擾，扮咩呀死肥撚"},{"pid":"0cd7607cf33a5afdd3212c50a417516cbc7b2259","tid":717741,"uid":10495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:17:56.000Z","msg":"仲諗緊女客點樣可以變性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4731f15c36ec0db6392e1d2213e17c3792e751e","tid":717741,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:57:37.000Z","msg":"用托盤要佢自己攞。"},{"pid":"d02ca9e4774b3572989ea04767eef1c58896dcaa","tid":717741,"uid":55011,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T09:58:55.000Z","msg":"之前買早餐找錢個姐姐都成日掂我隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 性騷擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82fe797218729ac10732e9a9751ab9f20a945f7b","tid":717741,"uid":192004,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:00:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db9f734d33dcf0cc8d01742c2c1d25a376ec2b8a","tid":717741,"uid":81507,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/180432_fadb77f52de9c3a7b9d79c686ea6c367.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F180432_fadb77f52de9c3a7b9d79c686ea6c367.png&h=60cfb8ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b89233c67c2d0dbb32733f97f04e4eafdb8f18a","tid":717741,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T11:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce58f0a3ce4816f28f1dabbd77468bbb5334f4c5","tid":717741,"uid":42188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T11:35:3